{"tid":2130103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"山頂地盤疑播毒 攻陷觀塘辦公室  堅城建築群組 激爆17個案","createTime":"2020-07-29T04:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T04:46:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e690ca612cfbf62b0adf94f88cf9a67a14cf4e19","tid":2130103,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:43:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/local/20200729/ZIWDGRARBMC6CA5JKR6OGBBEKI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2FZIWDGRARBMC6CA5JKR6OGBBEKI%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6SL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=5f6d885b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2FZIWDGRARBMC6CA5JKR6OGBBEKI%2F&h=c2e4b821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/local/20200729/ZIWDGRARBMC6CA5JKR6OGBBEKI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n山頂地盤疑播毒 攻陷觀塘辦公室 <br />\n堅城建築群組 激爆17個案<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】辦公室位於觀塘創紀之城3期的堅城（梁氏）建築有限公司，有17名員工及家屬感染武肺。堅城是山頂加列山道一豪宅項目的承建商，衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，員工曾在觀塘辦公室內沒有戴口罩，亦有一同用膳，未知與該山頂地盤工人確診個案是否關連。<br />\n<br />\n截至前日，堅城群組已有13人確診，涉及6男7女，年齡介乎3歲至69歲，當中四人早於25日確診，餘下四人及五人分別在26日及前日確診。最早發病是一名60歲男患者，20日發病後，25日確診。他住在坑口富寧花園6座，資料。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/O5rBBPoVGsrkB4lLUMxHrgnsjpI=/1761x1174/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WF7TSL274C6ERGZERAWZSH4QYE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FO5rBBPoVGsrkB4lLUMxHrgnsjpI%3D%2F1761x1174%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWF7TSL274C6ERGZERAWZSH4QYE.gif&h=6b90ccf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n堅城位於山頂加列山道的豪宅地盤爆出多個確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有患者仍未入院<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：疫情會無公佈 張竹君︰講漏咗<br />\n<br />\n其他患者。。。。。。。。。。資料顯示昨日仍等未入院。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君於疫情簡報會上表示，堅城建築群組昨日錄得兩宗新增確診及兩宗初步確診個案，意味群組規模已增至17人。染疫員工於觀塘創紀之城辦公室工作，部份人在辦公室沒有戴口罩，亦有人一同用餐，有密切接觸，目前仍未了解確診員工是否曾到地盤工作，或者其他個別地盤確診個案是否有關連，而該公司有20多名員工，會送往檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘區區議員梁翊婷表示，據指堅城位於山頂加列山道的豪宅地盤有工人確診，但不知涉及多少人。張竹君則指，會跟進群組是否與加列山道地盤有關。<br />\n<br />\n堅城建築的母公司承。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8Sds2Fbcz35NRT1SSNw3OnssS_8=/894x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FFCCJECU2UYL2TYGOVBXON4VU4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8Sds2Fbcz35NRT1SSNw3OnssS_8%3D%2F894x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFFCCJECU2UYL2TYGOVBXON4VU4.gif&h=63d4b71e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地盤上周六起已停工，現只有一名保安員看守。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地盤保安︰工人馬路邊吃飯<br />\n<br />\n本報記者昨午到加列山。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n其他地盤亦有確診個案，張竹君指，個案分佈西九龍和大圍，啟德則有兩名扎鐵工人確診，亦有散工和搬運工人的個案，但形容地盤個案「散收收」，暫未有個別地盤有明顯多個案。<br />\n<br />\n保華建業本月25日。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n建造業扎鐵職工。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a07b2448a926a81eec649832797590446d434c0f","tid":2130103,"uid":19501,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"群組唔講，狗唔講，你不如唔好叫衛生署，叫PPRB啦"},{"pid":"9a9f702a52b07d2d3aeaf6a7c1d3ccad2c607c4d","tid":2130103,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6843a4ca4f40cfbfec15ae476a69474a2800d52","tid":2130103,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a07b2448a926a81eec649832797590446d434c0f","tid":2130103,"uid":19501,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"群組唔講，狗唔講，你不如唔好叫衛生署，叫PPRB啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce8a1f694960ebcf1ba20eb242a85dccaebdfde","tid":2130103,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:46:29.000Z","msg":"地盤佬一定唔戴罩 一定會群組爆出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}